#. Used as HTML title of the page
#: firefox/features/memory.lang:6
msgid "Firefox Browser: Use less memory, get more speed"
msgstr "Y Porwr Firefox: Defnyddio llai o gof a chael mwy o gyflymder"

#. Used as HTML description of the page
#: firefox/features/memory.lang:11
msgid ""
"Is your computer slow? Your browser might be using too much memory. Switch "
"to Firefox today for more speed."
msgstr ""
"A yw eich cyfrifiadur yn araf? Efallai bod eich porwr yn defnyddio gormod o "
"gof. Newidiwch i Firefox heddiw am fwy o gyflymder."

#: firefox/features/memory.lang:15
msgid "Less memory usage than Chrome"
msgstr "Llai o ddefnydd o gof na Chrome"

#: firefox/features/memory.lang:19
msgid "If your web browser uses too much memory, switch to Firefox."
msgstr "Os yw eich porwr gwe'n defnyddio gormod o gof, newidiwch i Firefox."

#: firefox/features/memory.lang:23
msgid "Speed up your computer"
msgstr "Cyflymwch eich cyfrifiadur"

#: firefox/features/memory.lang:27
msgid ""
"Every computer program you run takes up some memory. When too much is used, "
"your system can slooooowww down. Firefox aims for a balance — using enough "
"memory to let you browse smoothly and leaving plenty of memory to keep your "
"computer responsive."
msgstr ""
"Mae pob rhaglen cyfrifiadur rydych yn ei defnyddio yn cymryd peth cof. Pan "
"mae gormod yn cael ei ddefnyddio, gall eich system araaaaafu. Mae Firefox y "
"anelu at gytbwysedd — defnyddio digon o gof i chi gael pori'n llyfn a gadael "
"digon o gof i gadw eich cyfrifiadur i fod yn ymatebol."

#: firefox/features/memory.lang:31
msgid "Stop running out of memory"
msgstr "Peidio rhedeg allan o gof"

#: firefox/features/memory.lang:35
msgid ""
"<a href=\"%(url)s\">Chrome uses up to 1.77x more memory than Firefox</a>. If "
"your computer is already low on memory, this can cause a significant "
"slowdown. Using Firefox’s latest version with multi-process can result in "
"more available memory to run your favorite programs."
msgstr ""
"Mae <a href=\"%(url)s\">Chrome yn defnyddio 1.77x yn fwy o gof na Firefox</"
"a>. Os yw eich cyfrifiadur eisoes yn isel ar gof, gall hyn achosi arafwch "
"arwyddocaol. Gall defnyddio'r fersiwn diweddaraf o Firefox gyda'r prosesau "
"lluosog arwain at gael mwy o gof ar gael ei redeg eich hoff raglenni."

#: firefox/features/memory.lang:39
msgid "Browse faster, privately"
msgstr "Pori'n gynt, yn breifat"

#: firefox/features/memory.lang:43
msgid ""
"Explore the web faster with <a href=\"%(url)s\">Firefox Private Browsing</"
"a>. Only Firefox’s private mode includes tracking protection which blocks "
"ads with trackers from loading on pages. Decluttering sites means web pages "
"can load faster."
msgstr ""
"Gallwch grwydro'r we'n gynt gyda <a href=\"%(url)s\">Pori Preifat Firefox</"
"a>. Dim ond modd preifat Firefox sy'n cynnwys diogelwch rhag tracio sy'n "
"rhwystro hysbysebion sydd â thracwyr rhag llwytho ar dudalennau. Mae glanhau "
"tudalennau'n golygu bod tudalennau gwe'n angor yn gynt."
